title: Dick interviews George Shearing
description:
Dick Robinson, your host of American Standards by the Sea, interviews the great George Shearing about his choice to move to America and the chance comment in the 'tube' that started it all.

If you like this clip, please join us for more fun at http://www.yachtamusic.com!
